Package org.codeoverflow.chatoverflow.api.io.input

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    FileInput
    Input that allows you to perform file operations that would otherwise be prohibited by the sandbox security manager.
    It features easy ways to read different types of files
    Input
    A input connects to a service by using a connector to receive data
    RconInput  
    SampleInput
    An example for an input, for implementation see SampleInputImpl in the framework
    SerialInput
    Connects to a device that is connected to your pc through a serial port (an Arduino for example) to receive data
